0.4 Preview patchnotes
======================

- squid no longer spawning in water (use essence if you need them)
- soulus updated:
  * TOP support added
  * new way to get some essences: https://github.com/Yuudaari/soulus#spawning-slimes-magma-cubes-and-iron-golems- 
  * Enderlink (teleporter) added: https://github.com/Yuudaari/soulus#enderlink-
  * Soul totem (Chunkloader/Fake player multiblock structure) recipe altered to fit into the modpack

new mods: betterfps, hopperducts
removed mods: anima mundi
